Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Cambiar Estado de Mesa
PATCH http://{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tables/1/status?status=AVAILABLE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### Eliminar Mesa
DELETE http://{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/tables/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

