### =====================================
### 5. ENDPOINTS ADMIN - PRODUCTOS Y RECETAS
### =====================================

### ========== PASO 0: CREAR ITEMS PRIMERO (INGREDIENTES) ==========
### IMPORTANTE: Los items deben crearse ANTES de las recetas

### Crear Item - Carne Molida
POST http://{{baseUrl}}/api/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Carne Molida",
  "description": "Carne de res molida 80/20",
  "unitOfMeasurement": "kg",
  "expirationDays": 15,
  "itemCategoryId": 11
}

### Crear Item - Queso
POST http://{{baseUrl}}/api/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Queso Amarillo",
  "description": "Queso slice",
  "unitOfMeasurement": "unit",
  "expirationDays": 30,
  "itemCategoryId": 2
}

### Crear Item - Lechuga
POST http://{{baseUrl}}/api/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Lechuga",
  "description": "Lechuga fresca",
  "unitOfMeasurement": "kg",
  "expirationDays": 5,
  "itemCategoryId": 3
}

### ========== PASO 1: CREAR RECETAS CON LOS ITEMS ==========
### Ahora que existen los items, crear las recetas
### Importante: Especificar itemDetails con itemId, quantity, isOptional

### Crear Recipe para Hamburguesa (CON itemDetails)
POST http://{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/recipes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Receta Hamburguesa Clásica",
  "quantity": 1,
  "description": "Ingredientes para hacer una hamburguesa",
  "itemDetails": [
    {
      "itemId": 1,
      "quantity": 100,
      "annotation": "Picada fina",
      "isOptional": false
    },
    {
      "itemId": 2,
      "quantity": 1,
      "annotation": "Queso amarillo",
      "isOptional": true
    },
    {
      "itemId": 3,
      "quantity": 2,
      "annotation": "Hojitas frescas",
      "isOptional": true
    }
  ]
}

### Crear Recipe para Pizza
POST http://{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/recipes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Receta Pizza Margherita",
  "quantity": 1,
  "description": "Ingredientes para pizza",
  "itemDetails": [
    {
      "itemId": 1,
      "quantity": 200,
      "annotation": "Como salsa base",
      "isOptional": false
    },
    {
      "itemId": 2,
      "quantity": 2,
      "annotation": "Mozzarella",
      "isOptional": false
    }
  ]
}

### Obtener todas las recetas
GET http://{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/recipes
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Obtener receta específica por ID
GET http://{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/recipes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Actualizar receta
PUT http://{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/recipes/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "name": "Receta Hamburguesa Mejorada",
  "quantity": 1,
  "description": "Ingredientes mejorados"
}

### Eliminar receta
DELETE http://{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/recipes/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

